article_title: Grade the Denver Broncos’ performance vs. the Oakland Raiders – The Denver Post
article_text: Rockies manager Walt Weiss tinkered with his lineup before Thursday’s game against Boston, dropping rookie shortstop Trevor Story from second to seventh and moving DJ LeMahieu up to the second spot.
